Description: The Semantic Web Dog Food (SWDF)i s the reference linked dataset of the Semantic Web community about papers- people- organisations- and events related to its academic conferences. Scholarlydata dataset (https://w3id.org/scholarlydata) is a refactoring of SWDF. We use a novel data model (conference-ontology) which improves the Semantic Web Conference Ontology- adopting best ontology design practices. To add conference to this dataset we provide an open source maintenance workflow https://github.com/AnLiGentile/cLODg
Sources: Web:Absent Name:Andrea Giovanni Nuzzolese; Anna Lisa Gentile Email:gentile.annalisa@gmail.com
